{
  "stem": "11723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you know that you're Jewish, but you can never, ever tell anybody that you're Jewish because you'll get killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was, of course, drilled already for weeks as to what my name was, where my father was, who my mother was, and all the prayers, the Protestant prayers, and the songs, and Christmas songs, and everything.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I knew it by heart like you wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was also told not to cry, not to make a big scene, because we don't want the neighbors to know that you're being taken away permanently.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, they didn't say permanently, but for a long period of time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Mommy and Daddy will come and get you when everything is OK.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, I wasn't yet four years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I, I really didn't know what it meant to be dead or killed, but I knew it was something horrible.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember this woman picked me up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I had a small suitcase.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she took the suitcase in one hand, me in the other hand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she told my mother, don't come with us to the tram stop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she was heading towards the tram.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was looking back over her shoulder and I saw my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my mother was, like, hiding From-- she was following us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And from house to house, she would duck into the entrances of the houses so she thought I didn't see her, but I did.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I could see that she was crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we got on the tram, and I saw her from the tram.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was holding on to this woman like for dear life, because I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where am I going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What am I doing here?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
